data.description: Remarkable 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2-story traditional home located in the heart of Great Bridge. Home is under 10 years old, and is designed with both modern elegance and family comfort in mind. The kitchen is a true centerpiece, featuring a charming farm sink, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient sit-up bar and dining area. Step out through the sliding glass door into the expansive backyard, complete with a wooded privacy fence, ensuring a perfect blend of nature and seclusion. Situated in a prime location, near local shopping, restaurants, schools, and offers a convenient commute with easy access to nearby interstates. Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your home.
